This paper is about network bandwidth and latency provisioning in the datacenter, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI) and data centers (cs.DC). The paper also discusses policies for resource allocation and configuration, which could fall under systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the need for security and protection against denial-of-service attacks, which could fall under cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper evaluates its approach using simulations, which could fall under performance (cs.PF).
